{"tid":470553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"房署公屋停車場明年將加租 林寶平治法拉利公屋車主：那有錢","createTime":"2017-11-16T11:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T11:55:03.000Z","uid":39539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24d01aebc8599d556539a4b9293c50f2712b3d86","tid":470553,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"房委會轄下的商業樓宇小組委員會周一將召開會議，商討明年停車場收費。消息指，房屋署進行市場研究後，建議明年1月1日起調高逾151個停車場、約3萬個泊車位的月租<br />\n當中私家車月租泊車位平均加幅約6%，有蓋泊車位月租收費加至$1,550至$2,730；露天泊車位月租收費加至$1,270至$2,250，車主每月需多付$70至$150。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/195014_de5df768f30e8a580e0e76e8de97a7ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F195014_de5df768f30e8a580e0e76e8de97a7ae.jpg&h=d2dc0c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/195053_b12df5d14491042b7c013a4b5c86f1a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F195053_b12df5d14491042b7c013a4b5c86f1a3.jpg&h=28fb12f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36b4ff2762c1251f192cbb29f55c9d9f7f06c7fd","tid":470553,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"因應車價收租仲好啦"},{"pid":"fe64e9de3dd6ff9a625c3214adf9ee8b011a658a","tid":470553,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因應車價收租仲好啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger"}]}